Mission.Author: KingRaptor
Mission.Description: Kite, burn and race across Comet Catcher in this challenging arena!
Mission.Name: Super Extreme Kodachi Rally
Mission.ScoringMethod: Earn points by killing mexes and bosses, and for completing rounds. Try not to take too long or lose your units!

TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action (Alternate)
TriggerLogic.CodeStr: local units = GG.mission.FindUnitsInGroup("Intro2") for unitID in pairs(units) do Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, CMD.FIRE_STATE, {0}, 0) Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, 36214, {0}, 0) -- disable tactical AI end

TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action (Alternate)
TriggerLogic.CodeStr: if WG.Music then WG.Music.SetWarThreshold(0) WG.Music.SetPeaceThreshold(-1) end

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Welcome back folks to another episode of SUPER EXTREME KODACHI RALLY!
Burn mexes! Torch raiders! KILL ANYONE WHO GETS IN YOUR WAY!

TriggerLogic.CodeStr: local units = GG.mission.FindUnitsInGroup("Intro2") for unitID in pairs(units) do Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, CMD.FIRE_STATE, {2}, 0) end
local unitID = GG.mission.FindUnitInGroup("Koda") if unitID then Spring.MoveCtrl.Enable(unitID) end

TriggerLogic.Name: Add Objective
TriggerLogic.Description: 1 Kodachi 3 mexes Enemies: Glaives Powerup every 45 seconds
TriggerLogic.Title: Round 1

TriggerLogic.Message: ROUND ONE! Get ready!

TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message:
Welcome to General Saktoth's Super Extreme Kodachi Rally (SEEKeR!)
Your objective in each round is to destroy all the mexes, while killing enemy raiders who give chase and outsmarting fixed defenses. Each level adds increasingly deadlier challenges, so stay on your toes!
To help you out, there are powerups scattered around the map. Touch them with a Kodachi to activate them. More powerups will spawn at regular intervals.
If all your Kodachis are dead, you lose the round. Don't worry, you get to try again!

TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action (Alternate)
TriggerLogic.CodeStr: -- reset defense ranges Spring.SendCommands("luaui togglewidget Defense Range Zero-K") Spring.SendCommands("luaui togglewidget Defense Range Zero-K")

TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action (Alternate)
TriggerLogic.CodeStr: GG.EndRound() local units = GG.mission.FindUnitsInGroup("Koda") for unitID in pairs(units) do GG.SetUnitInvulnerable(unitID, true) end
